{"tid":460751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【出醜國際】中國選手輸咗 狂毆瑞士單車隊成員","createTime":"2017-11-07T02:25:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-07T03:02:23.000Z","uid":39464,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0723a170e8780a1a879529f7931f7ab549d63b90","tid":460751,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T02:25:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171106/large/1509982580_f9d7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171106%2Flarge%2F1509982580_f9d7.jpg&h=24ff4801&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n瑞士《一瞥報》（Blick）報道，在中國環海南島國際公路單車賽第7賽段，上周五（3日）在萬寧興隆舉行，一名中國車手因懷疑被瑞士國家隊的隊車絆倒，在終點對瑞士隊工作人員大打出手。當地報章批評事件令人難以置信，並上傳當日發生的施暴影片，在場的警察勸架也沒有用。<br />\n<br />\n中國科一LOOK洲際隊車手王鑫當日在比賽中摔倒，他質疑是瑞士隊隊車擦撞導致，賽後便向瑞士隊的工作人員當街施暴。過程被po上網後引發瑞士網民不滿，表示應該禁止王鑫參加國際比賽，也呼籲瑞士「不要容忍這一切」。<br />\n<br />\n而中國單車協會則在隔天發出聲明，表示對於暴力行為零容忍，已經決定取消科一LOOK洲際隊繼續參賽資格，並會進一步調查整個事件。<br />\n<br />\n中國科一LOOK洲際隊隨後在官方微信號發聲明，說明事情經過並向公眾道歉，還指事發當日，比賽裁判組已發出公告，對雙方隊員都有處理，因不聽從競賽裁判指揮，涉事瑞士國家隊領隊Hondo Danilo被判罰100瑞士法郎（約781港元）；中國科一LOOK隊領隊200瑞士法郎（約1562元）；因暴力行為，涉事中國科一LOOK隊隊員王鑫被取消比賽資格，並判罰200瑞士法郎。<br />\n<br />\n瑞士《一瞥報》/《環球時報》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171107/57425660\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171107%2F57425660&d=YLZVOCTtPfRM52Mv9ZxkNP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=f05da3e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171107%2F57425660&h=008015ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171107/57425660</a>"},{"pid":"fdd8611f7031c2c6793f0e096564d91d3d3848e4","tid":460751,"uid":389,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T02:26:43.000Z","msg":"運動員<br />\n<br />\n拳擊運動員"},{"pid":"1238f6c2baef796f81f4d5a6dfcb3f3581e51fb6","tid":460751,"uid":22227,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T02:27:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"26aec1f781ae33bc3f9a0cfebfa4fb1110d59061","tid":460751,"uid":32716,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T02:34:47.000Z","msg":"當街施暴&hellip;<br />\n講到好似當街老強個工作人員咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cbba69b2aff1412d79e9f4af437eee97876cceb","tid":460751,"uid":127583,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T02:36:09.000Z","msg":"我仲以為係往死裡打個篇嘢"},{"pid":"496c1e9aee9a4cccb225ee8de1b300c3cbf77ee8","tid":460751,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T02:36:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>運動員<br />\n<br />\n拳擊運動員</blockquote><br />\n係武術散打先啱 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec0d39ba6fb4c60f5373f9990f10c819513f7b4c","tid":460751,"uid":128568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T02:39:58.000Z","msg":"咁細單野都上報,究竟係我地對呢D事件習以為常定瑞士見得少大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2a6658fb1465dceaa8472ebcab4890c72ee767c","tid":460751,"uid":82640,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T02:41:30.000Z","msg":"支那黎講都係咁上下<br />\n次次北上都要保持戰鬥狀態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb0bca5d6854ef62f4228390e43f093129114a5f","tid":460751,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T02:47:38.000Z","msg":"禁鳩支那選手就啱啦"},{"pid":"db1395b12d0a2405c288553a5c65664fea8e795d","tid":460751,"uid":40723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T02:50:23.000Z","msg":"試吓對手係俄仔，睇佢敢唔敢郁人"},{"pid":"46e6806444ea013d51e47f7f16e1172229ee46f6","tid":460751,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T02:52:20.000Z","msg":"支那特色<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f382ef6941eb08b81f3